data.description: Looking for a home in Foxbank Plantation for less than $300k?  Look no further!  Welcome home to this beautiful property that is nestled in the quiet subsection of Breakwater, with lovely neighbors and beautiful greenspace.  Upon entry into this home, you will be greeted by a large, open family room, featuring a gas fireplace and large, picturesque windows. LVP flooring are throughout the downstairs space, making the home perfect for entertaining!  The family room is open to the kitchen, with countertops and cabinets a-plenty! Not to mention, new HVAC installed (2020).Upstairs, you will find 3 large bedrooms, including the master bedroom, with an en-suite and a tub/shower combo.  2 additional bedrooms share an enormous hall bathroom. The laundry room is conveniently located upstairThe backyard is accessible through the kitchen with a large, sliding-glass doors.  The yard is massive - it's begging for an inground pool!    Foxbank Elementary is just a bike-ride away; plus this neighborhood doesn't disappoint!  A 67-acre lake plus another 13 ponds location throughout; not to mention the resort-style living at the pool and on-sight fitness and amenities center.    This neighborhood offers more than you can imagine! Don't let this one get away!
